{"tid":723387,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非法擴展範圍 元朗「B仔涼粉」被取消牌照","createTime":"2018-06-30T10:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T14:37:24.000Z","uid":37554,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"41d65fb602b0d39ead5e8dc24e79dedbf5c6da57","tid":723387,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:56:58.000Z","msg":"食環署表示，位於元朗又新街56號置富中心地下3、4及7號舖的「佳記甜品」，今年2月因非法擴展營業範圍被法庭8次定罪，屢次違反《食物業規例》，今日被食環署署長取消牌照。<br />\n<br />\n食環署發言人表示，食肆持牌人因違例事項，今年2月8次被法庭定罪，共罰款3.2萬，署方亦根據違例記分制記下持牌人180分，食肆因此被取消牌照。發言人提醒食物業處所持牌人必須遵守《食物業規例》，否則牌照可能被暫時吊銷或取消。"},{"pid":"60e313987080c460f9399491765ed072374ef5a8","tid":723387,"uid":16451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:03:02.000Z","msg":"抵佢啦 成條路比佢霸哂"},{"pid":"d58ebae6c97e7a5ab31a6fc7a116f3ae86a53c54","tid":723387,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:05:03.000Z","msg":"真係恭喜晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a99848c86c5b6e16fc76f4714003bcaaa2cd9d","tid":723387,"uid":46835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:05:58.000Z","msg":"咪以為黑底真係可以大晒，抵你有今日呀!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f676ea5d55d97211c75e505d50dd398440726e","tid":723387,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:06:07.000Z","msg":"收皮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb78a88515d6e5fe9a6c664122d4262ebae732b3","tid":723387,"uid":84282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:07:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"699b949ce722f38330850b19239d8714333ee3f7","tid":723387,"uid":31371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:50:48.000Z","msg":"垃圾b仔 正評不解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ced4622c08e71630425ad9a4f14fd8dd6757941","tid":723387,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor